~ sleep_mode
set screen = "sleep"
=>< snippets/focus_conversation
do Character.play_audio("task0_sleep_mode_intro")
Sam: The computer wants us to yawn out loud to tell it to turn down the lights if we want to sleep! Let’s see if it works. [next=4]
do Character.play_audio("listen_and_repeat")
