~ blast_off
set screen = "idle"
do Player.move_to(1)
do Character.move_to(1)
do Character.play_audio("task0_blast_off_intro")
=>< snippets/focus_conversation
Sam: You did it! You’re working really hard at this – Great Job! Now that our spaceship is full of fuel and the computer knows your voice, it’s time to find Planet Stardust!  Our handy dandy computer will countdown to blast off. Listen closely and then repeat what you hear to send us into space! [next=12]


